\section{The College of Air Magics (Ver 2.1)}
\label{college:air}
\index{colleges!Air Magics|(}

\begin{multicols}{3}
d15 11
a25 8
\textbf{Traditional Colours:} Air Mages traditionally dress in blues
and greys. Due to their habit of being outdoors in all weathers,
Adepts of this college tend to wear practical clothing and avoid long
trailing cloaks or skirts.

\textbf{Traditional Symbols:} Given the ephemeral nature of their
element, Air Mages have little use for symbols, usually allowing their
traditional colours to advertise their profession.
