@d824 1
a824 1
\sItem{Duration}{Special}
d835 14
a848 8
Upon a sucessful cast of this ritual the Adept summons an Air
Elemental from the elemental plane of Air.  The Elemental will appear
within 20 feet of the Adept. The Elemental will remain until banished,
or until it has an Air Special Counterspell cast on it by the
Adept. Conjured Air Elementals will normally obey their Summoner, but
will generally be indifferent to all Non-Elemental entities.  Should
the ritual fail nothing will occur.  If the ritual backfires an Air
Elemental will turn up and immediately attack the summoner.
