\sItem{Storage}{Investment, Ward, Magical Trap}
d835 8
a842 9
With this Ritual, the Adept conjures an Air Elemental from the
elemental plane of Air.  The Elemental will appear within 20 feet of
the Adept. The Elemental will remain until banished, or until it has
an Air Special Counterspell cast on it by the Adept. Conjured Air
Elementals will be mildly annoyed with their Summoners and may attack,
but will generally be indifferent to all Non-Elemental entities.  The
summoning is always successful but unless the ritual is successfully
cast then it will arrive uncontrolled.

